{"tid":389624,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行驟變夕陽？德銀講明機械人取代大量員工 (19:16)","createTime":"2017-09-06T11:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T04:52:53.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c42867e58ebed233609bec63dafca074ebdfbed","tid":389624,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170906/img/20170906191659fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170906%2Fimg%2F20170906191659fi_p1.jpg&h=1877f16a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=rZaTRMfadQqdAKnAKRuUSpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e36d3c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】銀行業已驟變夕陽行業？外國傳媒報道，德意志銀行行政總裁John Cryan警告，「大量」員工最終將會被機械人及其他科技所取代。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，在新世代下，傳統的會計師及銀行家猶如「算盤」，這「算盤世代」將會終結。他說：「在德銀，我們有員工的行為像機械人，做着一些機械化的事情，將來角色將會互換。我們需要想新的方法招聘員工，或許員工需要找新的方法去消磨時間... 故此，最滿意的答案是我們不再需要那麼多員工。」<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，德銀現時在全球擁有大約10萬名員工，雖然John Cryan沒有具體指出機械人取代員工的數目，但已經以「大量」的字眼來形容。<br />\n<br />\n他又說：「我們需要承認過去擁有的是美好，但這不適用於未來。我們需要更多革命精神。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，隨着人工智能(AI)日漸進步，已有機械人服務員出現，不少國際大型銀行已陸續在分行引入新技術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170906/20170906191659fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170906%2F20170906191659fi.html&d=rZaTRMfadQqdAKnAKRuUSpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2035c62d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170906/20170906191659fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e78f2a36d0f76fa37ddc54bf9d70babbc6cd590","tid":389624,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"合理"},{"pid":"a4ef4f92b19c4f89183bff40ba8d414fc2f5f7ed","tid":389624,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"第一步都係炒it先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf80ae1913ef898866dc1da63303609b0a11168","tid":389624,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:45:14.000Z","msg":"人類退場時代越來越近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ef4cefa67ab63d884c9e5461fdd6561d214abc","tid":389624,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"係就快啦<br />\n最好聽日"},{"pid":"eb22333f1584526bab9517d02d5dcba5d8fce7f7","tid":389624,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:52:53.000Z","msg":"銀行將會出現大量女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}